	(27156, 2, 0, 'Yes, yes, I haven\'t forgotten Hyjal, or Silithus, or the march of the Legion, or every other damnable confrontation the 7th Legion has faced. It... I don\'t want the soldiers to hear this, Two-bit, but for the first time in my life...', 12, 0, 100, 1, 0, 0, 'Text 3'),
